<emphasis id="B922FD3B4B16FF9814F9D692FF0AF80B" box="[136,234,1995,2021]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="44">Remarks</emphasis>
: 
<bibRefCitation id="EFC75CD84B16FF981486D692FE31F80B" author="Cosson, E. S. - Ch." box="[247,465,1995,2021]" pageId="13" pageNumber="44" pagination="144 - 145" refId="ref8308" refString="Cosson, E. S. - Ch. (1866) Chronique Horticole (premiere quinzaine d'abril). Revue Horticole (Paris) 37: 144 - 145. [https: // www. biodiversitylibrary. org / item / 196547  page / 179 / mode / 1 up]" type="journal article" year="1866">Cosson (1866: 144)</bibRefCitation>
mentioned a concrete gathering in the protologue of 
<taxonomicName id="4C565AAA4B16FF981069D692FA83F80B" authorityName="Cosson, K" authorityYear="1866" box="[1048,1379,1995,2021]" class="Pinopsida" family="Pinaceae" genus="Abies" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pinales" pageId="13" pageNumber="44" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="pinsapo" variety="baborensis">
<emphasis id="B922FD3B4B16FF981069D692FB55F80B" box="[1048,1205,1995,2021]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="44">Abies pinsapo</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="B922FD3B4B16FF981098D692FA83F80B" box="[1257,1379,1995,2021]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="44">baborensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
: “[…] Muséum d’histoire naturelle […] De magnifiques échantillons, munis de cones développés, ont été publiés, en 1861, par les soins de M. Kralik, conservateur de mes collections et l’un des collaborateurs habituels de mes explorations en 
<collectingCountry id="F34161B94B15FF9B14F9D19BFF00FF32" box="[136,224,194,220]" name="Algeria" pageId="14" pageNumber="45">Algérie</collectingCountry>
. La plante, dans un 
<emphasis id="B922FD3B4B15FF9B15B3D19AFDCFFF32" box="[450,559,195,220]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="45">Exsiccata</emphasis>
édité par lui sous le nom de 
<emphasis id="B922FD3B4B15FF9B1707D19BFB54FF32" box="[886,1204,194,220]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="45">Plantae Algeriensis selectae</emphasis>
, porte le nº 144 et est déterminée par moi 
<taxonomicName id="4C565AAA4B15FF9B151BD1BFFDE8FEEE" authorityName="Boissier, G" authorityYear="1838" box="[362,520,230,256]" class="Pinopsida" family="Pinaceae" genus="Abies" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pinales" pageId="14" pageNumber="45" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pinsapo">
<emphasis id="B922FD3B4B15FF9B151BD1BFFDE8FEEE" box="[362,520,230,256]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="45">Abies pinsapo</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C565AAA4B15FF9B1667D1BEFD24FEEE" authorityName="Cosson, K" authorityYear="1866" box="[534,708,230,257]" class="Pinopsida" family="Pinaceae" genus="Abies" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pinales" pageId="14" pageNumber="45" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="pinsapo" variety="baborensis">
var. 
<emphasis id="B922FD3B4B15FF9B1636D1BFFD24FEEE" box="[583,708,230,256]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="45">Baborensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Les échantillons ont été recueillis, le 
<date id="FFE807E94B15FF9B1005D1BFFAFAFEEE" box="[1140,1306,230,256]" pageId="14" pageNumber="45" value="1861-07-21">21 juillet 1861</date>
, par MM. A. Letourneux, H. de la Perraudière, Kralik et moi, ainsi que par M. Lambert”.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BE921294B15FF9B14CCD076FF46FD62" blockId="14.[136,1452,158,652]" pageId="14" pageNumber="45">
We have found several specimens at K, VTA, and P belonging to the gathering cited in the protologue, and therefore can be treated as 
<typeStatus id="54ED9F8B4B15FF9B15C4D00AFDFBFE83" box="[437,539,339,365]" pageId="14" pageNumber="45">syntypes</typeStatus>
. The specimens with barcodes K000076230, K000076228 (
<figureCitation id="136D3DAC4B15FF9B10C9D00BFB1CFE82" box="[1208,1276,338,364]" captionStart="FIGURE 8" captionStartId="13.[136,229,1494,1516]" captionTargetBox="[335,1253,190,1470]" captionTargetId="figure-22@13.[335,1253,190,1470]" captionTargetPageId="13" captionText="FIGURE 8. Lectotype of Abies pinsapo var. baborensis Cosson, K (barcode K000076228). Photography courtesy of Herbarium K; reproduced with permission." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6605328" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6605328/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="45">Fig. 8</figureCitation>
), K000076226, P00507233, P00507234, P00507235, P00507236, P01636208, and VTA067017, contain the printed original label of the exsiccatum, annotated as: “ 
<collectorName id="26A344FF4B15FF9B1595D0C3FDB4FE5A" box="[484,596,410,436]" pageId="14" pageNumber="45">L. Kralik.</collectorName>
–Plantae Algerienses selectae. / 144. 
<taxonomicName id="4C565AAA4B15FF9B178BD0C3FB08FE5A" authority="Boiss." authorityName="Boissier, G" authorityYear="1838" box="[1018,1256,410,436]" class="Pinopsida" family="Pinaceae" genus="Abies" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pinales" pageId="14" pageNumber="45" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pinsapo">Abies Pinsapo Boiss.</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicName id="4C565AAA4B15FF9B109ED0C2FA7CFE5A" authorityName="Cosson, K" authorityYear="1866" box="[1263,1436,410,437]" class="Pinopsida" family="Pinaceae" genus="Abies" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pinales" pageId="14" pageNumber="45" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="pinsapo" variety="baborensis">var. Baborensis</taxonomicName>
/ (Coss.) / In regione sylvatica superior montium Babor et / Tababor Kabyliae orientalis / 
<date id="FFE807E94B15FF9B101BD0E7FAE8FE36" box="[1130,1288,446,472]" pageId="14" pageNumber="45" value="1861-07-21">
<collectingDate id="EFACFE014B15FF9B101BD0E7FAE8FE36" box="[1130,1288,446,472]" pageId="14" pageNumber="45" value="1861-07-21">21 Julio 1861</collectingDate>
</date>
”. 
<location id="8E8977F24B15FF9B116FD0E7FAA0FE36" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03FF903F4B16FF9B14F9D767FF46FD62:8E8977F24B15FF9B116FD0E7FAA0FE36" box="[1310,1344,446,472]" country="Algeria" county="It" municipality="In" name="On" pageId="14" pageNumber="45" stateProvince="Constantine">On</location>
the other hand, the specimen with barcode K000076225 bears a label annotated as: “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C565AAA4B15FF9B1789D0BBFB11FE12" authority="Boiss." authorityName="Boissier, G" authorityYear="1838" box="[1016,1265,482,508]" class="Pinopsida" family="Pinaceae" genus="Abies" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pinales" pageId="14" pageNumber="45" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pinsapo">Abies Pinsapo Boiss.</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicName id="4C565AAA4B15FF9B108AD0BAFA4BFE12" authorityName="Cosson, K" authorityYear="1866" box="[1275,1451,482,509]" class="Pinopsida" family="Pinaceae" genus="Abies" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pinales" pageId="14" pageNumber="45" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="pinsapo" variety="baborensis">var. Baborensis</taxonomicName>
Coss. / Baborensis / Djebel Tababor. / petite Kabylie, prov. de 
<collectingRegion id="4992EFCB4B15FF9B1723D35FFC3BFDCE" box="[850,987,518,544]" country="Algeria" name="Constantine" pageId="14" pageNumber="45">Constantine</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F34161B94B15FF9B1797D35FFBDEFDCE" box="[998,1086,518,544]" name="Algeria" pageId="14" pageNumber="45">Algèrie</collectingCountry>
. / 
<collectorName id="26A344FF4B15FF9B1028D35EFB2FFDCE" box="[1113,1231,518,545]" pageId="14" pageNumber="45">E. Cosson</collectorName>
, 21 Juill. 1861”. 
<collectingMunicipality id="6B8DBB534B15FF9B11E5D35EFA4BFDCF" box="[1428,1451,519,545]" pageId="14" pageNumber="45">In</collectingMunicipality>
conclusion, we designate the specimen with barcode K000076228 as the 
<typeStatus id="54ED9F8B4B15FF9B17B4D373FBCCFDAA" box="[965,1068,554,580]" pageId="14" pageNumber="45">lectotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C565AAA4B15FF9B1023D373FA44FDAA" authorityName="Cosson, K" authorityYear="1866" box="[1106,1444,554,581]" class="Pinopsida" family="Pinaceae" genus="Abies" kingdom="Plantae" order="Pinales" pageId="14" pageNumber="45" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="pinsapo" variety="baborensis">
<emphasis id="B922FD3B4B15FF9B1023D373FB12FDAA" box="[1106,1266,554,580]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="45">Abies pinsapo</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="B922FD3B4B15FF9B115BD373FA44FDAA" box="[1322,1444,554,580]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="45">baborensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<collectingCounty id="628859A54B15FF9B14F9D316FF79FD87" box="[136,153,591,617]" pageId="14" pageNumber="45">It</collectingCounty>
is the most complete and informative specimen of the exsiccatum number 144 collected by 
<collectorName id="26A344FF4B15FF9B10DBD316FAF2FD86" box="[1194,1298,590,617]" pageId="14" pageNumber="45">L. Kralik</collectorName>
in 1861 (
<figureCitation id="136D3DAC4B15FF9B110FD317FF76FD62" captionStart="FIGURE 8" captionStartId="13.[136,229,1494,1516]" captionTargetBox="[335,1253,190,1470]" captionTargetId="figure-22@13.[335,1253,190,1470]" captionTargetPageId="13" captionText="FIGURE 8. Lectotype of Abies pinsapo var. baborensis Cosson, K (barcode K000076228). Photography courtesy of Herbarium K; reproduced with permission." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6605328" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6605328/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="45">Fig. 8</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
